test_even_range:
assert [6, 8, 10, 12, 14] == [8, 10, 12, 14]
  At index 0 diff: 6 != 8
  Left contains one more item: 14
  Full diff:
  - [8, 10, 12, 14]
  + [6, 8, 10, 12, 14]
  ?  +++
test_large_range:
assert [3, 4, 5, 6, 7] == [4, 5, 6, 7]
  At index 0 diff: 3 != 4
  Left contains one more item: 7
  Full diff:
  - [4, 5, 6, 7]
  + [3, 4, 5, 6, 7]
  ?  +++
